Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想問幾個問題\N\N並證明一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有問題就先摘下眼罩\N\N報上姓名來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「霸王流」正統傳人\N\N海蒂{\fnsimhei}·{\r}E{\fnsimhei}·{\r}S{\fnsimhei}·{\r}英格瓦特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,──自稱「霸王」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是最近那位暴力狂徒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不否認
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想問我些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是關於你知己的「王」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖王奧利維耶與\N\N冥府炎王伊克斯威莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該知道她們的行蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不認識什麼\N\N聖王或冥王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.92,0:01:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我僅認識兩位\N\N真摯而普通的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事我會另想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此外 我要證明一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的拳與我的拳\N\N究竟誰才更強大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你裝備防護服與武裝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才用不著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細看看 居然是個孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要做這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了證明自己的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你還有幾下子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎嵐之鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.37,Faqi,NTP,0,0,0,,Start Up{\fs22}\N\N{\fs52}啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了證明自己的強大？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且 我必須比現在更加強大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就別做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認真去練習\N\N或成為專業格鬥家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別在這裡賣弄身手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會為你介紹\N\N健身館或道場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝你的厚意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我所追尋的\N\N力量與人生的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅存在於過去的曆史中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這麼遠便要出招？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是射擊系嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一個使命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,──戰勝列強諸「王」\N\N稱霸於貝爾卡的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我昔日的宿願
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說夢話了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去的諸王們都已死絕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倖存者與末裔們\N\N都和平地生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弱小的「王」還會有活著的價值嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝爾卡的戰亂也好\N\N聖王戰爭也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連貝爾卡本身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都早已結束在歷史中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捨棄防禦發動了這枷鎖！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我依然活在那段歷史中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\t(2000,5500,1,\bord6\\3c&HAACD66&)} {\fad(0,200)}霸王斷空拳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弱小便是罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弱小的拳 是無法守護任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的那一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好強烈的打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體是絕對強大的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的心太過弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武裝形態解除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去後休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒來後再...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能倒在這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎嵐之鋒你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:56.71,Faqi,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm OK.{\fs22}\N\N{\fs52}我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為我聯系昴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.55,Faqi,NTP,0,0,0,,All right.{\fs22}\N\N{\fs52}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好這裡是昴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 來幫我個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諾威 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打架時重重地挨了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對手是那位襲擊犯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也狠狠地給了她一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還悄悄留下了追蹤器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們快去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諾威 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到她了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給蒂婭去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的別這麼亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是個孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子似乎事出有因
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以先別帶她去警防署嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就先帶她去我的房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克勞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來都謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧利維耶...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我們還未分勝負呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你作為賢明的王\N\N帶領國民走向和平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願大地不再荒廢於戰火\N\N願青空與彩花祝福你的國度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你會...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去！ \N\N「搖籃」由我來...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧利維耶...讓我來...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧利維耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}奧利維耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夢...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最為悲傷的記憶...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎做了惡夢 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是...？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 諾威
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有自稱「霸王」英格瓦特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真名艾茵哈特{\fnsimhei}·{\r}斯崔特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖希爾達魔法學院\N\N中等科一年生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 保險櫃中的行李\N\N我都檢查過了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心 全都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然隨身帶著校服與學生證
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是個笨蛋暴徒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為正好在放學途中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會倒在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 大家早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早餐做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！ 培根煎蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蔬菜湯可以盡情喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 艾茵哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是昴{\fnsimhei}·{\r}中島
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能有很多話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一邊吃飯一邊說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先向你介紹一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是這家的主人 我的姐姐昴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一位救災隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是總局執行官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫蒂安娜{\fnsimhei}·{\r}蘭斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她們收留了你\N\N好好感謝她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是襲擊格鬥家的犯人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以解釋一下理由嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說太古的貝爾卡戰爭\N\N在她心中還尚未終結
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想證明自己的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有什麼來著...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 想揍聖王與冥王一頓是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後那句不太準確
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「霸王是古代貝爾卡最強之王」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想證明這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為無法容忍自己的弱小...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說你並非憎恨\N\N聖王家系與冥王家系嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎那就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為昴是兩位的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 快趁熱吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們稍後一起去警防署總局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好為你檢查一下身體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正並未接獲報案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要承諾不再在街頭滋事\N\N很快就可以回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是當事人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦波一切正常\N\N身體也沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此外 她的確是\N\N貝爾卡王族的末裔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在醫局中有她的登錄資料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登錄？ 為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 她是一位「記憶繼承者」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記憶繼承？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.90,0:13:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一種繼承了父母\N\N或先祖記憶的症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於案例罕見\N\N我們登錄了她的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個簡單的說是什麼意思呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也難以斷言究竟何等程度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她繼承了祖先的「王」\N\N克勞斯{\fnsimhei}·{\r}英格瓦特的記憶與知識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括他經驗過的\N\N各種經歷與感情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 繼承的記憶通常會逐漸淡忘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要今後不斷積累幸福記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不會再受過去記憶的困擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 蒂婭\N\N害你的假日泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你與貝爾卡的王還真有緣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒誇你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過艾茵哈特那孩子\N\N似乎有很多心事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總不能放著不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事便交給你的妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明還有很多事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太沒防備了 霸王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很快便會被釋放\N\N接下來有什麼打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是個假日吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會立刻回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:16:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的姐姐與蒂安娜\N\N在局員中也算高手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們認識很多\N\N熟知古代貝爾卡的專家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太明白你說的戰爭是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們很樂意為你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別去找聖王她們的麻煩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 也不錯嘛\N\N最好別去找麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只希望與高手對決\N\N變得更加強大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並以此證明「霸王流」的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經也很野蠻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是非常氣惱\N\N總是想付諸於暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並非喜歡打鬥或暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是不知道其他的樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你很喜愛格鬥技吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然還在修行\N\N也勉強還算個教練
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之... 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看得出你的才能與心境
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說錯了嗎？ \N\N你不喜歡它嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從未考慮過自己是否喜歡它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過霸王流是我人生的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟我說說霸王流的事嗎？ \N\N還有你的國度與記憶中的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好進行下一個項目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝克莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 諾威的短信？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲特媽媽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她正在沖涼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲特媽媽我可以一起洗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈葉也來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲特媽媽今天不就要出航了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們儘量多在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲特 今天我來為你洗頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 也別忘了我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克莉絲今天也很賣力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家對克莉絲的正式名稱\N\N說了些什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都說不出所料\N\N是個好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 幹嘛說悄悄話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣嘛 奈葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天在家吃午餐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.88,0:20:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我約了莉奧和珂羅娜\N\N在圖書館見面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圖書館？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯我想去查些資料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...應該就在這邊...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？ 找得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯... 不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 就是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:21:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「霸王英格瓦特傳」與「雄王列記」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有當時的歷史書！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝珂羅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是之前小露向我推薦的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為何突然關心\N\N「修圖拉」的曆史啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諾威說想一同學習這些歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霸王英格瓦特與聖王奧利維耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們曾經是怎樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是兩位充滿傳奇的王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同的書中有不同的見解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡也寫著 「現代歷史研究中\N\N兩者的關係尚無定論」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 聖王奧利維耶明明很有名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太不可思議了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 諾威剛認識了\N\N一位練習格鬥技的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約我們一起練習呢
